<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Course Purchase Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4b2994;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .course-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #4b2994;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #4b2994;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Course Purchase Successful!</h1>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Thank you for purchasing a course from us!</p>
            
            <div class="course-details">
                <h3>Course Details:</h3>
                <p><strong>Course ID:</strong> <%= _id %></p>
                <p><strong>Course Name:</strong> <%= name %></p>
                <p><strong>Purchase Price:</strong> $<%= price %></p>
                <p><strong>Purchase Date:</strong> <%= date %></p>
            </div>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="/courses/<%= _id %>" class="button">Start Learning</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>We're excited to have you start your learning journey with us! You can access your course immediately by clicking the button above or visiting your dashboard.</p>
            
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            
            <p>Happy Learning!<br>Your E-Learning Team</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Â© <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Your E-Learning Platform. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
